  <name>CD Ripper</name>
  <summary>Audio CD ripper with MusicBrainz tagging</summary>
  <description>
    <p>
      A no-nonsense audio CD ripper that produces verified FLAC files with
      MusicBrainz metadata, AccurateRip verification, embedded cover art,
      and synced lyrics from LRCLib.
    </p>
    <p>Features:</p>
    <ul>
      <li>libcdio-paranoia for sample-accurate reads</li>
      <li>MusicBrainz disc ID lookup with TOC-fuzzy fallback</li>
      <li>AccurateRip CRC verification</li>
      <li>Multi-disc / box-set aware track numbering</li>
      <li>Multi-drive parallel ripping</li>
      <li>Direct upload to WebDAV (Nextcloud) targets</li>
    </ul>
  </description>
  <launchable type="desktop-id">io.github.gravey158.cdripper.desktop</launchable>
